sentences: Jim Schwall (born November 12, 1942) is an American musician, singer-songwriter, and photographer.
Jim Schwall was born in Chicago, Illinois, and currently resides in Tucson, Arizona.
Schwall and Siegel formed a blues duo in 1964, playing at Chicago bars and clubs.
He holds a PhD in musical composition from the University of Wisconsin-Madison, 1993, and has taught music at the college level.
In 2002 he ran for mayor of Madison, Wisconsin.
